    </item>
    <item>
      <title>[인사] 금융감독원 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2025/12/23/ASNLDCTMIFCUDHN47CJ7YCPLA4/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2025/12/23/ASNLDCTMIFCUDHN47CJ7YCPLA4/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
